5000|$|A filter may be {{incompatible}} {{with the use of}} a <b>lens</b> <b>hood,</b> since not all filters have the required threading for a screw-in hood or will allow a clip-on hood to be attached. Adding a <b>lens</b> <b>hood</b> on top of one or more filters may space the hood away from the lens enough to cause some vignetting.|$|R
